OL,7,FBBC chairman Samir Shah is expected to
OL,8,Fapologise for the way a speech by
OL,9,FDonald Trump was edited for Panorama
OL,10,Fafter several days of pressure on the
OL,11,Fbroadcaster prompted the resignation
OL,12,Fof director-general Tim Davie.
OL,14,FThe chief executive of BBC News,
OL,15,FDeborah Turness, also announced her
OL,16,Fresignation on Sunday after the
OL,17,Fcorporation was accused of misleading
OL,18,Fthe public following claims that the
OL,19,Fspeech had been selectively edited in
OL,20,Fthe documentary, Trump: A Second
OL,21,FChance?
