OL,7,FA memo by Michael Prescott, a former
OL,8,Fexternal adviser to the BBC's
OL,9,Feditorial standards committee, raised
OL,10,Fconcerns in the summer about the way
OL,11,Fclips of the US president's speech on
OL,12,FJanuary 6 2021 were spliced together
OL,13,Fin Trump: A Second Chance? to make it
OL,14,Fappear he had told supporters he was
OL,15,Fgoing to walk to the US Capitol with
OL,16,Fthem to "fight like hell".
