OL,7,FCritics said the documentary,
OL,8,Fbroadcast by the BBC the week before
OL,9,Flast year's US election, was
OL,10,Fmisleading and removed a section where
OL,11,Fthe US president said he wanted
OL,12,Fsupporters to demonstrate peacefully.
OL,14,FMr Shah is expected to apologise and
OL,15,Fprovide further details on the
OL,16,FPanorama episode on Monday in his
OL,17,Fresponse to the Culture Media and
OL,18,FSport Committee which asked how he
OL,19,Fwould address the concerns.
