OL,7,FMr Shah said Sunday was a "sad day"
OL,8,Ffor the BBC while committee chairwoman
OL,9,FDame Caroline Dinenage said Mr Davie's
OL,10,Fresignation was "regrettable" but
OL,11,F"restoring trust in the corporation
OL,12,Fmust come first".
OL,14,FMr Davie said his departure will not
OL,15,Fbe immediate and that he is "working
OL,16,Fthrough" timings to ensure an "orderly
OL,17,Ftransition" over the coming months,
OL,18,Fwhile Ms Turness said controversy
OL,19,Faround the Panorama edit had "reached
OL,20,Fa stage where it is causing damage to
OL,21,Fthe BBC ` an institution that I love".
