OL,7,FIn a statement sent to staff, Mr Davie
OL,8,Fsaid his resignation was "entirely"
OL,9,Fhis decision and he was "thankful" to
OL,10,Fthe chairman and board for their
OL,11,F"unswerving and unanimous support"
OL,12,Fduring his tenure.
OL,14,FHe said: "Like all public
OL,15,Forganisations, the BBC is not perfect,
OL,16,Fand we must always be open,
OL,17,Ftransparent and accountable."
