OL,7,FThe Culture Secretary Lisa Nandy
OL,8,Fthanked Mr Davie for his "service to
OL,9,Fpublic service broadcasting" and for
OL,10,Fleading the BBC through a period of
OL,11,F"significant change".
OL,13,FShe said the Government will support
OL,14,Fthe BBC board through the transition
OL,15,Fand the upcoming charter review will
OL,16,Fhelp the corporation to adapt to a new
OL,17,Fera that "secures its role at the
OL,18,Fheart of national life for decades to
OL,19,Fcome".
