OL,7,FThe BBC's Royal Charter, which expires
OL,8,Fat the end of 2027, sets out the
OL,9,Fcorporation's mission, public purposes
OL,10,Fand funding.
OL,12,FMs Nandy said in November last year
OL,13,Fthat the Government would use the
OL,14,Freview of the charter to consider
OL,15,Falternative ways of funding the
OL,16,Fcorporation but ruled out the licence
OL,17,Ffee being replaced by general taxation.
