OL,7,FMs Turness, who has been in the role
OL,8,Fsince 2022, said that she had offered
OL,9,Fher resignation to Mr Davie on
OL,10,FSaturday night adding that, despite
OL,11,Fmistakes being made, the "recent
OL,12,Fallegations that BBC News is
OL,13,Finstitutionally biased are wrong".
OL,15,FIn a message sent to staff, she said
OL,16,Fshe was "proud" of the work they had
OL,17,Fdone adding: "The ongoing controversy
OL,18,Faround the Panorama on President Trump
OL,19,Fhas reached a stage where it is
OL,20,Fcausing damage to the BBC ` an
OL,21,Finstitution that I love.
