OL,7,F"In public life leaders need to be
OL,8,Ffully accountable, and that is why I
OL,9,Fam stepping down."
OL,11,FThe BBC has been criticised for a
OL,12,Fnumber of failings in recent months
OL,13,Fwhich include breaching its own
OL,14,Faccuracy editorial guidelines,
OL,15,Flivestreaming the controversial Bob
OL,16,FVylan Glastonbury set, as well as
OL,17,Fmisconduct allegations surrounding
OL,18,Fformer MasterChef presenter Gregg
OL,19,FWallace.
